data.description: This one-story brick home exudes charm and elegance, offering the perfect blend of comfort and style. The open floor plan will captivate you, creating a seamless flow throughout the home. One of the highlights of this grand home is the fantastic owner-bedroom suite, boasting not one but two walk-in closets to accommodate even the most extensive wardrobes. This home also features two additional bedrooms, two full bathrooms, a spacious kitchen with plenty of cabinet space, a charming fireplace, vaulted ceilings, an attached garage, and a great back deck where you can take in the serene surroundings.
